snippet.title: I Am Jesus Christ - Wait Until You See Priest Simulator (OMGH)
snippet.description:
I Am Jesus Christ has turned a lot of heads for being an apparent Son of God simulator. Wander as Jesus and do first-person miracles? Fight Satan? Walk on water? I'm in. 

Then there's Priest Simulator, which we look at in the latter end of the video. Whoever PlayWay S.A. are, they have some bizarre stuff under their umbrella. 

#IAmJesusChrist #Jesus #Simulator #JimSterling #OMGH #Trailer

The You Testament footage: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u9wytLm8tWY
